# [[still]]; [[yet]]; {{n-g|indicates that the phenomenon or observation still exists or the action is still ongoing}}
#: {{zh-x|他 還 沒 來。|He hasn't come '''yet'''.}}
#: {{zh-x|還 未 得 住。|It's '''still''' not OK.|C-T|tr='''van3''' mei5 ak2 zi5.}}
